# Retest C — Four-form common-mode-rejection structure

Eval-layer revalidation. Research-grade. Measurement only; verdict deferred to user.

Scripts (all under `scratch/_revalidation/retestC/`):
- `retestC_common_mode.py` — main per-fixture harness (137-pt grids, float64 path
